"title": "2540: Jesus Christ, genealogy of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2540: jesus christ, genealogy of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ's human ancestry is traced back in two separate lines to David and thence back to Adam. Jesus' descent from David is of importance for his Messianic claims.</p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from Adam</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23-Luke3:38\">LUK 3:23–3:38</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from Abraham</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:16\">GAL 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:25-Acts3:26\">ACT 3:25–3:26</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from Isaac</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:12\">GEN 21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:2-Gen26:4\">GEN 26:2–26:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:16\">GAL 3:16</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from Jacob</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:13-Gen28:14\">GEN 28:13–28:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:2\">MAT 1:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:34\">LUK 3:34</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from the tribe of Judah</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:14\">HEB 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:18-Ruth4:22\">RUT 4:18–4:22</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from Jesse</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:1\">ISA 11:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:12\">ROM 15:12</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is descended from David</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's human lineage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:1-Matt1:17\">MAT 1:1–1:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:4\">LUK 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr3:10-1Chr3:19\">1CH 3:10–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23-Luke3:31\">LUK 3:23–3:31</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as the Son of David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:30-Matt20:31\">MAT 20:30–20:31</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:47-Mark10:48\">MRK 10:47–10:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:38-Luke18:39\">LUK 18:38–18:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:9\">MAT 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:15\">MAT 21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:27\">LUK 1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:32\">LUK 1:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:42\">JHN 7:42</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is greater than David</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:41-Matt22:45\">MAT 22:41–22:45</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:35-Mark12:37\">MRK 12:35–12:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:41-Luke20:44\">LUK 20:41–20:44</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps110:1\">PSA 110:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:5\">REV 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:16\">REV 22:16</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is greater than Solomon</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:42\">MAT 12:42</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:31\">LUK 11:31</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as the son of Joseph and Mary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:55\">MAT 13:55</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:3\">MRK 6:3</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:42\">JHN 6:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:16\">MAT 1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:22\">LUK 4:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:45\">JHN 1:45</a></p>",
